#: src/Admin/LibraryPage.php:373
msgid "~80% of the safe area. Mid-point between Safe and Max — clearly visible logo with a bit of scan headroom."
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/LibraryPage.php:374
#: src/Block/Maker.php:171
msgid "Max"
msgstr ""

#: src/Admin/LibraryPage.php:374
msgid "Full safe area for the chosen error correction. Largest logo the QR can support without losing scannability under good conditions."
msgstr ""

